				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I would like to see an actual lay on hands aa skill for our pets, call it mend companion 2 or something, but one that functions like a pally of similiar level.  Give it the same time restrictions as lay on hands.  Make the cost 6 AA points, and have mend companion 1 as requirement.
<br />

<br />
Another one I would like to see, is an AA ability that would allow us to cast an increased duration mass group buff damage shield.  A shield that would last 36 or 40 minutes.  Something that would make MGB finally useful for us.  Make the cost 5 AA points, and MGB a requirement.  Or perhaps, allow us to MGB Burnout 5 on all summoned pets in the immediate vicinity; a range like MGB now for all other casters that use the skill.  The latter would be MGB required, and cost an additional 3 points.
<br />

<br />
I would also like to see us get the chance to land critical heals on our pets.  Yes, I know this has gone round and round already, but now it could actually happen.  A single rank in the skill.  A 3 percent chance each cast or something.  Nothing grand, nothing that would occur every other time you cast it, but something that might happen when you need it most.  Make the cost 3 or 4 points.
<br />

<br />
Just a few things I would enjoy.
<br />

<br />
